name: SteamKeg - GPS / Real-Time Racing Games
blurb: Create exciting, GPS outdoor racing games featuring power-ups you play on your smart phone. It's kind of like Mario Kart in real life!

Platinum Membership \u2013 You will receive our coveted Platinum recognition plaque, hand crafted by a commissioned artist for display in your home or office. \r\n\r\nThe plaque will be framed and matted in SteamKeg\u2019s colors, and include a three dimensional platinum copy of your emblem displayed on our website and app. You will receive special space on our \u201cThank You\u201d page to display a personal picture of yourself or your organization, display a short personal message, and a link to your personal website. After we\u2019ve launched, you will receive free ad space for six months (rotating in-and-out along with the other platinum sponsors) on the dashboard of every game played world-wide. You will also receive first rights to continue this ad space there-after. There are only four Platinum awards being offered.
